<sect1 id="md_README_1autotoc_md2">
<title>Features</title><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><bold>Real-time Processing</bold>: Continuously monitors Zeek logs</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Graph Construction</bold>: Builds interactive network graphs with the following features<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><emphasis>Node level</emphasis>:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Degree (in/out/combined)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Temporal features (connection in the last minute and hour)</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><emphasis>Edge level (one edge per connection)</emphasis><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Source, target IP and port number</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Protocol, timestamp</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Host, Uri and HTTP method</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Version, user agent, status code</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Request and response body len</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Advanced Analysis</bold>:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Anomaly detection</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Traffic pattern recognition</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Connection profiling</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Real time Visualization</bold>:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Graphviz-based diagrams</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><bold>Alert System</bold>: Notifications for suspicious activities</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="md_README_1autotoc_md3">
