</programlisting></para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="md_README_1autotoc_md4">
<title>Installation</title><sect2 id="md_README_1autotoc_md5">
<title>Linux/maxOS</title><para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">git<sp/>clone<sp/>https://github.com/khoinhtvn/encryptedsummer</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cd<sp/>encryptedsummer/graph_builder</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">mkdir<sp/>build<sp/>&amp;&amp;<sp/>cd<sp/>build</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>..<sp/>-DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">make<sp/>-j$(nproc)</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="md_README_1autotoc_md6">
<title>Windows (Visual Studio)</title><para><programlisting filename=".shell"><codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>-G<sp/>&quot;Visual<sp/>Studio<sp/>17<sp/>2022&quot;<sp/>-A<sp/>x64<sp/>..</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">cmake<sp/>--build<sp/>.<sp/>--config<sp/>Release</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect2>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="md_README_1autotoc_md7">
<title>Usage</title><sect2 id="md_README_1autotoc_md8">
<title>Basic Analysis</title><para>The program checks for files in the specified path. It just processes files with known names (conn.log).</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".bash"><codeline><highlight class="normal">./graph_builder<sp/>/path/to/zeek/logs</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
